Description: Provides a pipeline for processing gas chromatographic data:
    automatic time-shift alignment (ATSA), sparsity-assisted signal smoothing
    (SASS), multiple baseline estimation algorithms with ensemble uncertainty
    quantification, peak detection and integration, and LOD/LOQ estimation.
    Designed for reproducible processing of single-channel GC signals from
    standard detectors.
